---
// Timeline section: vertical chronology + contact footer
// Uses only tokens.css custom properties; system fonts; zero external requests.
---

<section class="timeline-section">
  <p class="section-moral"><em>The tortoise kept a changelog.</em></p>

  <h2 id="timeline">Timeline</h2>

  <div class="timeline-container">
    <ol class="timeline-list">
      <li class="timeline-entry">
        <time class="timeline-date" datetime="2015">2015</time>
        <p class="timeline-text">Joined GitHub</p>
      </li>

      <li class="timeline-entry">
        <time class="timeline-date" datetime="2016">2016</time>
        <p class="timeline-text"><strong>Glimpse</strong> — iOS app (Objective-C)</p>
      </li>

      <li class="timeline-entry">
        <time class="timeline-date" datetime="2024/2026">~2024–2026</time>
        <p class="timeline-text"><strong>Tannery Row automation suite</strong> — operations toolbox, invoice bridge, sample-program tracker</p>
      </li>

      <li class="timeline-entry">
        <time class="timeline-date" datetime="2026-05">May 2026</time>
        <p class="timeline-text"><em>Claude Code Has a Memory Problem</em> — builds the Conductor memory layer</p>
      </li>

      <li class="timeline-entry">
        <time class="timeline-date" datetime="2026-06/2026-07">Jun–Jul 2026</time>
        <p class="timeline-text"><strong>Aesop</strong> open-sourced; 13 self-built waves, 130 PRs, v0.1.0-beta.4</p>
      </li>

      <li class="timeline-entry">
        <time class="timeline-date" datetime="2026-07">Jul 2026</time>
        <p class="timeline-text"><em>The System That Builds Itself</em> published; this portfolio assembled by the fleet</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-block" id="contact">
    <h3 class="contact-heading">Contact</h3>
    <ul class="contact-list">
      <li><span class="contact-label">Email</span> <a href="mailto:matt82198@gmail.com" class="contact-link">matt82198@gmail.com</a></li>
      <li><span class="contact-label">GitHub</span> <a href="https://github.com/matt82198" class="contact-link">github.com/matt82198</a></li>
      <li><span class="contact-label">Medium</span> <a href="https://medium.com/@matt82198" class="contact-link">medium.com/@matt82198</a></li>
      <li><span class="contact-label">LinkedIn</span> <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/matt-culliton-a8327676" class="contact-link">linkedin.com/in/matt-culliton-a8327676</a></li>
      <li><span class="contact-label">X</span> <a href="https://x.com/mculliton82198" class="contact-link">x.com/mculliton82198</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .timeline-section {
    max-width: var(--width-prose);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  }

  /* Override shared section h2 to adjust margin */
  .timeline-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .timeline-container {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .timeline-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Vertical line connecting timeline entries */
  .timeline-list::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 2.5rem;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .timeline-entry {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  /* Timeline dot */
  .timeline-entry::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 1.65rem;
    top: 0.35rem;
    width: 0.75rem;
    height: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--accent);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .timeline-entry::before {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  .timeline-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  }

  .timeline-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline-text strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .timeline-text em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  /* Contact block */
  .contact-block {
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .contact-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .contact-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 600;
    min-width: 5rem;
    text-align: right;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
    position: relative;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .contact-link:focus {
    outline: var(--focus-ring);
    outline-offset: var(--focus-ring-offset);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .contact-link {
      transition: none;
    }
  }

  /* Responsive: stack labels on small screens */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .contact-list li {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }

    .contact-label {
      text-align: left;
      min-width: unset;
    }

    .timeline-entry {
      padding-left: 4rem;
    }

    .timeline-list::before {
      left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-entry::before {
      left: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
